data.description: Are you ready to be impressed? Check out this custom home situated on a beautiful lot with HUGE mature trees! As soon as you enter the home, you'll notice the 2-Story ceilings finished with wood shiplap and the stone fireplace in the Living room, which also carries into the Kitchen & Dining room! 2 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms on the main level.  Upstairs is the PRIVATE Master bedroom (with vaulted wood ceilings) & suite! There is a balcony to enjoy the gorgeous yard & surroundings, the suite has shower, HUGE whirlpool tub & double vanity! The finished "Look-Out" basement has a Family room, 4th bedroom/office, rough-in for 4th bathroom & storage area. The garage is double deep & offers an un-finished room upstairs that could be possible related living space?  Great location near Aroma Park, nature trails and The Elks Country Club.
